		{
			"id": "d63d27f5-9542-4c2a-a457-7030fe1772d6",
			"name": "d63d27f5-9542-4c2a-a457-7030fe1772d6",
			"type": "facts",
			"content": {
				"number": "5",
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"55515\"></a>Ogynnsamma effekter vid be&shy;handling med <a class=\"index\" id=\"1061339\" data-text=\"kortikosteroider:biverkningar\"></a>kortikosteroider ",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h5 id=\"k4_48\"><span class=\"tab\"></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">V&auml;vnadsatrofi</span></h5>\r\n<p>Hudsk&ouml;rhet, muskelatrofi, osteoporos, aseptisk caputnekros i femur/humerus</p>\r\n<h5 id=\"k4_49\"><span class=\"tab\"></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Neurologiska/&ouml;gon</span></h5>\r\n<p>Benign intrakraniell hypertension, katarakt, glaukom</p>\r\n<h5 id=\"k4_50\"><span class=\"tab\"></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Metabola och endokrina</span></h5>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>F&ouml;rs&auml;mrad <span>glukostolerans</span>/diabetes mellitus, vikt&ouml;kning, bukfetma, tillv&auml;xth&auml;mning hos barn, sekund&auml;r binjurebarkssvikt<br><br></li>\r\n<li>Relaterade till mineralkortikoideffekten: v&auml;tske&shy;retention och &ouml;dem, kaliumf&ouml;rluster</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Vid uts&auml;ttning av farmakologisk behandling: terti&auml;r binjurebarksvikt</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5 id=\"k4_51\"><span class=\"tab\"></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Gastrointestinala</span></h5>\r\n<p>Vid samtidig behandling med NSAID kan risken f&ouml;r ulcus &ouml;ka</p>\r\n<h5 id=\"k4_52\"><span class=\"tab\"></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Psykiatriska</span></h5>\r\n<p>Eufori, s&ouml;mnrubbning, depression, mani</p>\r\n<h5 id=\"k4_53\"><span class=\"tab\"></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Cirkulation</span></h5>\r\n<p>Hypertoni</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p></p>",
