				"number": "10",
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"78791\"></a>Symtom och kliniska fynd vid  <a class=\"index\" id=\"1061629\" data-text=\"akromegali:symtom\"></a>akromegali ",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span>Huvudv&auml;rk, svettningar, snarkningar, s&ouml;mnapn&eacute;, akne</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>F&ouml;rstoring av h&auml;nder, f&ouml;tter, n&auml;sa, tunga, l&auml;ppar, l&aring;ngvuxenhet hos barn och ungdomar</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>F&ouml;rgrovade anletsdrag, underbett, stakett&auml;nder</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Hypertoni, nedsatt <span>glukostolerans<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"> eller diabetes mellitus</span><br></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Artros, spinalstenos, karpaltunnelsyndrom</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Allm&auml;n organf&ouml;rstoring: tyreoidea (struma), hj&auml;rta, njurar, lever, mj&auml;lte</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Kardiomyopati</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Kolonpolyper</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>",
