				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span>Ansiktsrundning, &ldquo;buffalo hump&rdquo;, supraklavi&shy;kul&auml;r utfyllnad, bukfetma</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Hirsutism, akne, r&ouml;d ansiktsf&auml;rg, striae, atrofisk hud, bl&aring;m&auml;rken, h&aring;ravfall</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Muskelsvaghet/atrofi, osteoporos, kotfrakturer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Hypertoni, nedsatt <span>glukostolerans</span>/diabetes mellitus, hypokalemi (framf&ouml;r allt ektopisk Cushing)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Minskad libido, impotens, menstruationsrubb&shy;ningar</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>S&ouml;mnst&ouml;rningar, psykiska besv&auml;r</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>H&auml;mmad l&auml;ngdtillv&auml;xt hos barn i kombination med &ouml;kande vikt</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>",
