				"number": "13",
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"14967\"></a>Diagnoskriterier för SIADH",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span>Hyponatremi, P/S-Na &lt;&nbsp;135 mmol/l</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span>S&auml;nkt P/S-osmolalitet &lt;&nbsp;275 mOsm/kg</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span>Urinosmolalitet &gt;&nbsp;100 mOsm/kg <br>Onormalt h&ouml;g urinkoncentration f&ouml;r den l&aring;ga <br>P/S-osmolaliteten</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span>Euvolemi<br>Patient utan tecken p&aring; &ouml;dem eller hypovolemi med l&aring;gt blodtryck, ortostatism och takykardi</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span>U-Na &gt;&nbsp;40 mmol/l &ndash; <span class=\"tab\"></span>Taget fr&aring;n stickprov <br>(ej samling)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px; margin:0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span>Annan trolig orsak till hyponatremi<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"> kan uteslutas</span><br>Fr&auml;mst uttalad hypotyreos, binjurebarkssvikt, p&aring;g&aring;ende diuretikabehandling eller njursjuk&shy;dom</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p></p>",
